  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428780/extras/b1fab9863d1a0ff34707f5d1dd051ff0.poster.avif?t=1707761053\" width=550 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428780/extras/b1fab9863d1a0ff34707f5d1dd051ff0.webm?t=1707761053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428780/extras/b1fab9863d1a0ff34707f5d1dd051ff0.mp4?t=1707761053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Pan Pan Boom Boom!</strong></h2>Face hordes of zombie in this black and white, top down shooter! Alone or in local coop, annihilate everything -and everyone- that stands in your way in order to make a safe exit from Zombie Camp!<br>Camp Zombie is a cooperative arcade game with a fun and immediate concept, incorporating some mechanics from a zombie mode with the easy handling of a top-down shooter, all with a unique graphical style!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428780/extras/e4d6d7855f7144ef3107cdb3bfe02bb0.poster.avif?t=1707761053\" width=550 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428780/extras/e4d6d7855f7144ef3107cdb3bfe02bb0.webm?t=1707761053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428780/extras/e4d6d7855f7144ef3107cdb3bfe02bb0.mp4?t=1707761053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Explore the multiple rooms to increase your firepower and purchase every single boost to match the ever increasing waves of zombies! Beware, however, as darkness might become an even bigger problem that those putrid foes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428780/extras/4cebe08b29fb2a0c2e172330cdaec7ef.poster.avif?t=1707761053\" width=550 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428780/extras/4cebe08b29fb2a0c2e172330cdaec7ef.webm?t=1707761053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428780/extras/4cebe08b29fb2a0c2e172330cdaec7ef.mp4?t=1707761053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A word from the manager!</strong></h2>In our post-apocalyptic zombie world, will you be able to survive my life-threatening, hyper-modern escape game? Try your best not to die, or be prepared to become zombies for the next challengers!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428780/extras/f1b29328a24b73a4c05f0a856ad2f1bc.poster.avif?t=1707761053\" width=550 height=138 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428780/extras/f1b29328a24b73a4c05f0a856ad2f1bc.webm?t=1707761053\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428780/extras/f1b29328a24b73a4c05f0a856ad2f1bc.mp4?t=1707761053\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Please note, you must connect at least one controller to play local multiplayer.",
